0.06_1    2014-08-19
 - Moo -> Moose
 - add no indirect 'fatal'
 - Zone IDs are updated per each batch of updates so online changes to DNS
   don't cause problems
 - Failures are handled per DNS record update
 - Rewrite to be resilient and fault tolerant. Failures of any expected type
   handled without dying
 - Rewrite to use CloudFlare::Client
 - Use IP lookup services in a random order
 - Use Dist::Zilla to build

